Allow to set a pre-plan or T-shirt size estimate that reflects rough, initial estimates for backlog items before people flesh out the item with child stories and add more detailed estimates. This estimate should, unlike the original estimate that is already available, be independent of the child estimates, it should not aggregate over an items children but rather be an independent value that captures the initial estimate.

